hadiths[55]{hadithnumber,text}:
4988,"Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) key beton Hazrat Salma aur Yaala Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath gaey. hamarey sath hamara eik sathi bhi tha. wo kisi dusrey musalman sey lad pada. us aadmi ney uskey bazu par daant gaad diye. us ney bazu uskey munh sey khincha to sath daant bhi nikal aaya. wo aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya aur diyat dilwaney ka mutalba karney laga. aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs apney bhai ko ja kar is tarah kaat'taa hai jaisey oont chabaataa hai. phir aa kar diyat maangna shuru kar deta hai? is (tarah key daanton) ki koi diyat nahin. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey daant ka koi moawza na dilwaya."
4989,Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney dusrey aadmi key bazu par kaat khaya jis sey us ka samney wala daant ukhad gaya. wo aap key paas (diyat leney key liye) aaya to aap ney usey rayegaan qarar diya (us ka koi moawza nahin dilwaya).
4990,Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney dusrey aadmi key bazu par kaat khaya jis sey us ka samney wala daant ukhad gaya. wo aap key paas (diyat leney key liye) aaya to aap ney usey rayegaan qarar diya (us ka koi moawza nahin dilwaya).
4991,Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke unhoney eik shakhs ko naukar rakha. wo kisi aadmi sey lad pada aur us ka haath kaat khaya. sath hi daant bhi ukhad gaya. wo ye muqadma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat mein ley gaya. aap ney farmaya : kya wo apna haath (terey munh mein) chhod deta ke to usey oont ki tarah chabaataa rehta?
4992,Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke unhoney eik shakhs ko naukar rakha. wo kisi aadmi sey lad pada aur us ka haath kaat khaya. sath hi daant bhi ukhad gaya. wo ye muqadma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat mein ley gaya. aap ney farmaya : kya wo apna haath (terey munh mein) chhod deta ke to usey oont ki tarah chabaataa rehta?
4993,"Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath jang ko gaya to mainey eik shakhs naukar rakh liya. phir mera naukar kisi aadmi sey lad pada. us aadmi ney usey kaat khaya yahan tak ke us ka samney wala daant gir gaya. wo shakhs Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap key samney ye baat zikr ki. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney isey rayegaan qarar diya (is ka koi moawza na dilwaya)."
4994,"Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath jang ko gaya to mainey eik shakhs naukar rakh liya. phir mera naukar kisi aadmi sey lad pada. us aadmi ney usey kaat khaya yahan tak ke us ka samney wala daant gir gaya. wo shakhs Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap key samney ye baat zikr ki. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney isey rayegaan qarar diya (is ka koi moawza na dilwaya)."
4995,"Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tangi waley lashkar mein gaya aur merey nazdik mera ye amal sab sey afzal amal hai. wahan mera eik naukar kisi aadmi sey lad pada. un mein sey kisi eik ney dusrey ki ungli par daant gaad diya. us ney jo ungli kheenchi to sath hi daant bhi ukhad aaya. doosra shakhs Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to aap ney usey koi moawza na dilwaya balke farmaya : kya wo apna haath terey munh mein diye rakhta ke to usey chabaa daalta?"
4996,"Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tangi waley lashkar mein gaya aur merey nazdik mera ye amal sab sey afzal amal hai. wahan mera eik naukar kisi aadmi sey lad pada. un mein sey kisi eik ney dusrey ki ungli par daant gaad diya. us ney jo ungli kheenchi to sath hi daant bhi ukhad aaya. doosra shakhs Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to aap ney usey koi moawza na dilwaya balke farmaya : kya wo apna haath terey munh mein diye rakhta ke to usey chabaa daalta?"
4997,"Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey us shakhs key barey mein jisney sathi ko kaat khaya tha aur us ka daant ukhad gaya tha, sabiqa (pichhli) riwayat ki tarah bayan hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : tujhey koi diyat nahin milegi."
4998,"Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey us shakhs key barey mein jisney sathi ko kaat khaya tha aur us ka daant ukhad gaya tha, sabiqa (pichhli) riwayat ki tarah bayan hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : tujhey koi diyat nahin milegi."
4999,Hazrat Safwan bin Yaala ibne Muniyah sey riwayat hai ke merey walid Hazrat Yala ibne Muniyah (Raziallahu anhu) key eik naukar key bazu par eik dusrey shakhs ney daant gaad diye. us ney apna haath uskey munh sey khincha to us ka daant gir gaya. ye muqadma Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pesh huwa to aap ney us daant ka koi moawza na dilwaya balke farmaya : kya wo apna haath terey munh mein rakh chhodta ke to usey oont ki tarah chabaataa rehta.
5000,Hazrat Safwan bin Yaala ibne Muniyah sey riwayat hai ke merey walid Hazrat Yala ibne Muniyah (Raziallahu anhu) key eik naukar key bazu par eik dusrey shakhs ney daant gaad diye. us ney apna haath uskey munh sey khincha to us ka daant gir gaya. ye muqadma Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pesh huwa to aap ney us daant ka koi moawza na dilwaya balke farmaya : kya wo apna haath terey munh mein rakh chhodta ke to usey oont ki tarah chabaataa rehta.
5001,Hazrat Safwan bin Yaala sey riwayat hai ke merey walid ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath gaey. sath eik naukar bhi ley gaey. wo kisi aadmi sey lad pada. us aadmi ney uski kalaai par kaat liya. jab us ko takleef hui to usney zor sey haath khincha. sath hi daant bhi ukhad aaya. ye muqadma Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs apney bhai ki taraf badhta hai aur us ko is tarah kaat khata hai jaisey oont chabaataa hai. aap ney uskey daant ka koi moawza na dilwaya.
5002,Hazrat Safwan bin Yaala sey riwayat hai ke merey walid ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath gaey. sath eik naukar bhi ley gaey. wo kisi aadmi sey lad pada. us aadmi ney uski kalaai par kaat liya. jab us ko takleef hui to usney zor sey haath khincha. sath hi daant bhi ukhad aaya. ye muqadma Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs apney bhai ki taraf badhta hai aur us ko is tarah kaat khata hai jaisey oont chabaataa hai. aap ney uskey daant ka koi moawza na dilwaya.
5003,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) koi chiz taqseem farma rahey they ke eik aadmi aaya. aur (be-sabri mein) aap par ondha hi ho gaya. aap ney apney haath mein pakdi hui chhadi ki nauk us ko maar di. wo aadmi (halqe sey) nikal gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bhai ! idhar aa aur badla ley ley. us ney kaha : (nahin) balke mainey maaf kar diya."
5004,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) koi chiz taqseem farma rahey they ke eik aadmi aaya. aur (be-sabri mein) aap par ondha hi ho gaya. aap ney apney haath mein pakdi hui chhadi ki nauk us ko maar di. wo aadmi (halqe sey) nikal gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bhai ! idhar aa aur badla ley ley. us ney kaha : (nahin) balke mainey maaf kar diya."
5005,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) koi chiz taqseem farma rahey they ke eik aadmi (leney key liye) aap par ondha hi ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath mein pakdi hui eik chhadi sey usey kachoka lagaya to wo haaye-waaye karney laga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : idhar aa aur badla ley ley. us ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! (nahin) balke mainey maaf kar diya.
5006,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) koi chiz taqseem farma rahey they ke eik aadmi (leney key liye) aap par ondha hi ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath mein pakdi hui eik chhadi sey usey kachoka lagaya to wo haaye-waaye karney laga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : idhar aa aur badla ley ley. us ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! (nahin) balke mainey maaf kar diya.
5007,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat Abbas key jaahili daur key eik buzurg ko bura bhala kaha. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey thappad raseed kar diya. us aadmi key qabiley waley aaye aur kehney lagey : ye bhi unhen thappad maareyga jis tarah unhoney isey thappad maara hai yahan tak ke unhoney aslaha pehan liya. ye baat Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchi. aap member par chadhey aur farmaya : aey logo ! tum roey zamin par basney waley logon mein sey kis shakhs ko Allah Taala key nazdik ziyada moazziz aur mohtaram samajhtey ho? unhoney kaha : aap ko. aap ney farmaya : phir sun lo ! Abbas mujh sey hain aur main un sey hun. hamarey faut shuda aabaa-w ijdaad ko bura na kaho. is tarah tum hum mein sey zinda afrad ko takleef pahunchaogey. wo log aap key paas hazir huye aur kaha : hum aap ki narazi sey Allah Taala ki panah maangtey hain. (maaf farma dijiye aur) Allah Taala sey hamarey liye bakhshish ki dua farmaiye.
5008,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat Abbas key jaahili daur key eik buzurg ko bura bhala kaha. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey thappad raseed kar diya. us aadmi key qabiley waley aaye aur kehney lagey : ye bhi unhen thappad maareyga jis tarah unhoney isey thappad maara hai yahan tak ke unhoney aslaha pehan liya. ye baat Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchi. aap member par chadhey aur farmaya : aey logo ! tum roey zamin par basney waley logon mein sey kis shakhs ko Allah Taala key nazdik ziyada moazziz aur mohtaram samajhtey ho? unhoney kaha : aap ko. aap ney farmaya : phir sun lo ! Abbas mujh sey hain aur main un sey hun. hamarey faut shuda aabaa-w ijdaad ko bura na kaho. is tarah tum hum mein sey zinda afrad ko takleef pahunchaogey. wo log aap key paas hazir huye aur kaha : hum aap ki narazi sey Allah Taala ki panah maangtey hain. (maaf farma dijiye aur) Allah Taala sey hamarey liye bakhshish ki dua farmaiye.
5009,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath masjid mein betha kartey they. jab aap khadey hotey, hum bhi aap key sath khadey hotey eik din aap khadey huye, hum bhi aap key sath khadey huye yahan tak ke jab aap masjid key darmiyan pahunchey to eik aadmi aap ko mila. us ney peechhey sey aap ki chadar pakad kar kheenchi. aap ki chadar khurdari si thi, is liye aap ki gardan surkh ho gaee. wo shakhs kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! mujhey ye do oont (ghalla) laad dijiye. aap kon sa apney ya apney baap key maal sey detey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main haqiqat mein apney maal sey nahin deta aur main Allah Taala sey bakhshish talab karta hun (ke aisa ghalat aetiqad rakhun) lekin main tujhey kuchh bhi nahin dunga yahan tak ke to mujhey gardan sey chadar khinchney ka qisaas dey. us erabi (dehati) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main aap ko qisaas nahin dunga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen martaba aisey hi farmaya. wo (erabi (dehati)) har dafa yehi kehta tha : Allah ki qism ! main aap ko qisaas nahin dunga. hamney erabi (dehati) ki baaten sunin to hum tezi sey uski taraf badhey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein aatey dekha to farmaya : jo bhi shakhs meri aawaz sunta hai, main usey qism deta hun ke wo apni jagah sey harkat na karey yahan tak ke main usey ijazat dun. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey kaha : arey ! us ko eik oont par jau aur dusrey oont par khushk khajuren laad dey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (dusrey logon sey) farmaya : jao. chaley jao."
5010,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath masjid mein betha kartey they. jab aap khadey hotey, hum bhi aap key sath khadey hotey eik din aap khadey huye, hum bhi aap key sath khadey huye yahan tak ke jab aap masjid key darmiyan pahunchey to eik aadmi aap ko mila. us ney peechhey sey aap ki chadar pakad kar kheenchi. aap ki chadar khurdari si thi, is liye aap ki gardan surkh ho gaee. wo shakhs kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! mujhey ye do oont (ghalla) laad dijiye. aap kon sa apney ya apney baap key maal sey detey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main haqiqat mein apney maal sey nahin deta aur main Allah Taala sey bakhshish talab karta hun (ke aisa ghalat aetiqad rakhun) lekin main tujhey kuchh bhi nahin dunga yahan tak ke to mujhey gardan sey chadar khinchney ka qisaas dey. us erabi (dehati) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main aap ko qisaas nahin dunga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen martaba aisey hi farmaya. wo (erabi (dehati)) har dafa yehi kehta tha : Allah ki qism ! main aap ko qisaas nahin dunga. hamney erabi (dehati) ki baaten sunin to hum tezi sey uski taraf badhey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein aatey dekha to farmaya : jo bhi shakhs meri aawaz sunta hai, main usey qism deta hun ke wo apni jagah sey harkat na karey yahan tak ke main usey ijazat dun. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey kaha : arey ! us ko eik oont par jau aur dusrey oont par khushk khajuren laad dey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (dusrey logon sey) farmaya : jao. chaley jao."
5011,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni pak zaat sey qisaas dilaatey they.
5012,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni pak zaat sey qisaas dilaatey they.
5013,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abu-Jahm bin Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko sadqa leney key liye bheja. eik aadmi ney sadqa deney key barey mein jhagda kiya to Hazrat Abu-Jahm (Raziallahu anhu) ney us ko maara. wo log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamein qisaas chahiye. aap ney farmaya : tumhein itna moawza deta hun. wo razi na huye. aap ney farmaya : achchha tum itna (aur) ley lo. aakhir wo razi ho gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main logon key samney khutba dey kar unhein tumharey razi honey ki khabar deta hun. unhoney kaha : theek hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba irshad farmaya : ye log merey paas qisaas leney aaye they. mainey unhein itney maal ki pesh kaash! ki to ye razi ho gaey hain. lekin wo log kehney lagey : hum razi nahin. muhajrin ney in ko saza deney ka irada kiya lekin aap ney in ko rok diya. wo ruk gaey. aap ney phir in ko bulaya aur farmaya : kya tum ab razi ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : main phir logon sey khitab karunga aur unhein bataunga ke tum razi ho gaey ho. unhoney kaha : theek hai. aap ney logon sey khitab farmaya aur un sey puchha : tum razi ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan.
5014,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abu-Jahm bin Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko sadqa leney key liye bheja. eik aadmi ney sadqa deney key barey mein jhagda kiya to Hazrat Abu-Jahm (Raziallahu anhu) ney us ko maara. wo log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamein qisaas chahiye. aap ney farmaya : tumhein itna moawza deta hun. wo razi na huye. aap ney farmaya : achchha tum itna (aur) ley lo. aakhir wo razi ho gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main logon key samney khutba dey kar unhein tumharey razi honey ki khabar deta hun. unhoney kaha : theek hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba irshad farmaya : ye log merey paas qisaas leney aaye they. mainey unhein itney maal ki pesh kaash! ki to ye razi ho gaey hain. lekin wo log kehney lagey : hum razi nahin. muhajrin ney in ko saza deney ka irada kiya lekin aap ney in ko rok diya. wo ruk gaey. aap ney phir in ko bulaya aur farmaya : kya tum ab razi ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : main phir logon sey khitab karunga aur unhein bataunga ke tum razi ho gaey ho. unhoney kaha : theek hai. aap ney logon sey khitab farmaya aur un sey puchha : tum razi ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan.
5015,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney eik ladki key kanon mein baaliyaan dekhin to (un ko hasil karney key liye) us ney ladki ko eik patthar sey maar dala. us bachchi ko Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to is mein kuchh jaan baqi thi. aap ney us sey puchha : tujhey falan ney qatl kiya hai? us ney sar key isharay sey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : falan ney qatl kiya hai? us ney sar key isharay sey kaha : nahin. aap ney phir (teesri baar) us sey puchha : kya tujhey falan ney qatl kiya hai? us ney sar key isharay sey kaha : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko bula bheja aur usey do pattharon key darmiyan qatl kar diya.
5016,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney eik ladki key kanon mein baaliyaan dekhin to (un ko hasil karney key liye) us ney ladki ko eik patthar sey maar dala. us bachchi ko Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to is mein kuchh jaan baqi thi. aap ney us sey puchha : tujhey falan ney qatl kiya hai? us ney sar key isharay sey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : falan ney qatl kiya hai? us ney sar key isharay sey kaha : nahin. aap ney phir (teesri baar) us sey puchha : kya tujhey falan ney qatl kiya hai? us ney sar key isharay sey kaha : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko bula bheja aur usey do pattharon key darmiyan qatl kar diya.
5017,Hazrat Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Khas'am qabiley ki taraf eik lashkar bheja. wo sajdey mein pad gaey taake jaan bacha saken lekin wo bhi maarey gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki nisf (aadhi) diyat ada farmaee aur farmaya : main har us musalman sey lataluq hun jo kafiron mein rehta hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khabrdar ! musalman aur kafir itney door rahen ke unhein eik dusrey ki aag nazar na aaye.
5018,Hazrat Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Khas'am qabiley ki taraf eik lashkar bheja. wo sajdey mein pad gaey taake jaan bacha saken lekin wo bhi maarey gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki nisf (aadhi) diyat ada farmaee aur farmaya : main har us musalman sey lataluq hun jo kafiron mein rehta hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khabrdar ! musalman aur kafir itney door rahen ke unhein eik dusrey ki aag nazar na aaye.
5019,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Bani-Israel mein sirf qisaas tha. diyat nahin thi. Allah Taala ney Quran Majeed mein ye aayat utaari : (کُتِبَ عَلَیْکُمُ الْقِصَاصُ فِی الْقَتْلٰی),''tum par maqtulon key barey mein barabar ka badla lena farz kiya gaya hai.'' azad key badley wohi azad (qatil) aur ghulam key badley wohi ghulam (qatil) aur aurat key badley wohi (qatil) aurat (qatl ki jaeygi). phir jis shakhs ko uskey bhai (maqtool key wali ) ki taraf sey kuchh maafi mil jaey to (maaf karney waley key liye) achchhey tareeqey sey diyat talab karna aur (qatil key liye) achchhey tareeqey sey adaegi karna hai. maafi sey murad ye hai ke jaan-boojh kar kiye gaye qatl ki surat mein maqtool ka wali diyat lena qubul kerey. ittiba bil-ma'aroof sey ye murad hai ke maqtool ka wali munasib andaz mein diyat wasul kar ley aur doosra fariq achchhey tareeqey sey adaegi kerey. (ذٰلِکَ تَخْفِیْفٌ مِّنْ رَّبِّکُمْ وَ رَحْمَۃٌ),''ye tumharey Rab ki taraf sey aasani aur rehmat hai.''yani ehle-kitab par nazil karda hukm key muqabley mein jo ke sirf qisaas tha aur diyat (ki gunjaaish) nahin thi."
5020,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Bani-Israel mein sirf qisaas tha. diyat nahin thi. Allah Taala ney Quran Majeed mein ye aayat utaari : (کُتِبَ عَلَیْکُمُ الْقِصَاصُ فِی الْقَتْلٰی),''tum par maqtulon key barey mein barabar ka badla lena farz kiya gaya hai.'' azad key badley wohi azad (qatil) aur ghulam key badley wohi ghulam (qatil) aur aurat key badley wohi (qatil) aurat (qatl ki jaeygi). phir jis shakhs ko uskey bhai (maqtool key wali ) ki taraf sey kuchh maafi mil jaey to (maaf karney waley key liye) achchhey tareeqey sey diyat talab karna aur (qatil key liye) achchhey tareeqey sey adaegi karna hai. maafi sey murad ye hai ke jaan-boojh kar kiye gaye qatl ki surat mein maqtool ka wali diyat lena qubul kerey. ittiba bil-ma'aroof sey ye murad hai ke maqtool ka wali munasib andaz mein diyat wasul kar ley aur doosra fariq achchhey tareeqey sey adaegi kerey. (ذٰلِکَ تَخْفِیْفٌ مِّنْ رَّبِّکُمْ وَ رَحْمَۃٌ),''ye tumharey Rab ki taraf sey aasani aur rehmat hai.''yani ehle-kitab par nazil karda hukm key muqabley mein jo ke sirf qisaas tha aur diyat (ki gunjaaish) nahin thi."
5021,"Hazrat Mujahid (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney aayat kareema (کُتِبَ عَلَیْکُمُ الْقِصَاصُ فِی الْقَتْلٰی … ),""tum par maqtulon key barey mein qisaas (barabar ka badla) lena farz kiya gaya hai, azad key badley wohi azad.'' key mutalliq mein farmaya : banu Israel key liye sirf qisaas ka hukm tha, diyat nahin thi. phir Allah Taala ney diyat ka hukm utaar kar is ummat key liye Bani-Israel key muqabley mein aasani farma di."
5022,"Hazrat Mujahid (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney aayat kareema (کُتِبَ عَلَیْکُمُ الْقِصَاصُ فِی الْقَتْلٰی … ),""tum par maqtulon key barey mein qisaas (barabar ka badla) lena farz kiya gaya hai, azad key badley wohi azad.'' key mutalliq mein farmaya : banu Israel key liye sirf qisaas ka hukm tha, diyat nahin thi. phir Allah Taala ney diyat ka hukm utaar kar is ummat key liye Bani-Israel key muqabley mein aasani farma di."
5023,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas qisaas ka eik muqadma aaya to aap ney maaf karney ka mashwara diya."
5024,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas qisaas ka eik muqadma aaya to aap ney maaf karney ka mashwara diya."
5025,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab bhi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas qisaas ka koi muqadma aaya aap ney maafi ka mashwara diya."
5026,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab bhi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas qisaas ka koi muqadma aaya aap ney maafi ka mashwara diya."
5027,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ka rishte-daar qatl kar diya jaey, usey do chizon mein sey behtar ka ikhtiyar hai : qisaas ley ley ya diyat."
5028,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ka rishte-daar qatl kar diya jaey, usey do chizon mein sey behtar ka ikhtiyar hai : qisaas ley ley ya diyat."
5029,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ka rishte-daar maara jaey, usey do mein sey behtar chiz ka ikhtiyar hai : qisaas ley ya diyat."
5030,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ka rishte-daar maara jaey, usey do mein sey behtar chiz ka ikhtiyar hai : qisaas ley ya diyat."
5031,Hazrat Abu-Salma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ka rishte-daar maara jaey. ye riwayat mursal hai.
5032,Hazrat Abu-Salma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ka rishte-daar maara jaey. ye riwayat mursal hai.
5033,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (qisaas key liye) ladney walon key liye munasib hai ke wo qisaas sey ruk jaeyn (jaldi na keren). warison mein maaf karney ka haq usey hai jo un mein sey ziyada qaribi ho, chahey wo aurat ho."
5034,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (qisaas key liye) ladney walon key liye munasib hai ke wo qisaas sey ruk jaeyn (jaldi na keren). warison mein maaf karney ka haq usey hai jo un mein sey ziyada qaribi ho, chahey wo aurat ho."
5035,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs andha dhund ladaai jhagdey (balwe aur hangaamey) main maara jaey jis mein patthar, kodey ya lathi ka aam istimal huwa to uski diyat qatle-khata (ghalti se huey qatl) ki diyat hogi. aur jis shakhs ko jaan boojh kar qatl kiya jaey, us ka qisaas liya jaeyga. jo shakhs qisaas mein rukawat baney, is par Allah Taala ki, farishton ki aur sab logon ki lanat hai. na us ka farz qubul na nafl."
5036,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs andha dhund ladaai jhagdey (balwe aur hangaamey) main maara jaey jis mein patthar, kodey ya lathi ka aam istimal huwa to uski diyat qatle-khata (ghalti se huey qatl) ki diyat hogi. aur jis shakhs ko jaan boojh kar qatl kiya jaey, us ka qisaas liya jaeyga. jo shakhs qisaas mein rukawat baney, is par Allah Taala ki, farishton ki aur sab logon ki lanat hai. na us ka farz qubul na nafl."
5037,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney marfooan bayan farmaya ke jo shakhs pattharon, kodon ya dandon ki andha dhund ladaai mein maara jaey to uski diyat qatle-khata (ghalti se huey qatl) wali hogi lekin jisey jaan boojh kar maara gaya, us ka qisaas liya jaeyga. aur jo shakhs qisaas mein rukawat baney, is par Allah taalaa, farishton aur sab logon ki taraf sey lanat. Allah Taala na us ka farz qubul farmaeyga na nafl."
5038,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney marfooan bayan farmaya ke jo shakhs pattharon, kodon ya dandon ki andha dhund ladaai mein maara jaey to uski diyat qatle-khata (ghalti se huey qatl) wali hogi lekin jisey jaan boojh kar maara gaya, us ka qisaas liya jaeyga. aur jo shakhs qisaas mein rukawat baney, is par Allah taalaa, farishton aur sab logon ki taraf sey lanat. Allah Taala na us ka farz qubul farmaeyga na nafl."
5039,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo ghalati sey maara jaey, shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein, yani kodey aur dandey waghera sey, uski diyat eik-sau oont hain jin mein sey chaalis hamila oontniyaan hongi."
5040,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo ghalati sey maara jaey, shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein, yani kodey aur dandey waghera sey, uski diyat eik-sau oont hain jin mein sey chaalis hamila oontniyaan hongi."
5041,Hazrat Qasim bin Rabeea ney mursal taur par bayan kiya hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka key din khutba irshad farmaya.
5042,Hazrat Qasim bin Rabeea ney mursal taur par bayan kiya hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka key din khutba irshad farmaya.
